                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 98.) I was sent for, and pro<lb></lb>duce the scales.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A woman offered me some money for a mat; which I would not take—I turned back—a boy ran up told, and me to hold the scales—the woman came up, and gave me in charge.</p>
